  </li>
  <li><strong>Ask for their advice.</strong>Â â€¨People want to help others and feel like theyâ€™re making a difference. Asking for their input will make them feel more valuable in the conversation while simultaneously stroking their ego.
    <ul>
      <li>â€œYou know Greg, Iâ€™m supposed to plan a first date with this girl I really like but Iâ€™m afraid of screwing it up. Where do you like to take your dates?â€</li>
