<p>Riz: Whatâ€™s up?
Keil: Washing your chicken just splatters the bacteria everywhere.</p>

<ul>
  <li><strong>Tease about love-life</strong> Inquire about their love life in a harmless way.Â â€¨It lets their guard down and shows youâ€™re willing to add humor into the conversation.
    <ul>
      <li>â€œWow Greg. You look pretty dapper. Hot date tonight?â€</li>
