    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Literally say â€œletâ€™s play the question gameâ€ where you get to ask each other any question and they have to respond (hint, this is a great and memorable thing to do on a first date).Â  Examples of good questions
    <ul>
      <li>What is something I donâ€™t know about you?Â </li>
      <li>What is something not many people know about you?Â  You said something about X the other (day/week/month), how is it?Â  Remember, this is a conversation.Â  You have to share too.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Match their energy, then add 10%.</p>
  </li>
  <li>Infuse Humour.</li>
